ygData.messageBody:
dont think i will be able to do that since i can only play like once a
week... n thats it... nothin more... (main reason: ill be using my office pc
to play when no one else is around, least during weekend i have excuse to do
that). But ill try real hard to join u guys... i do believe that the
leveling is exponential... so i should be able to catch up with u guys
sooner or later.... :)
dont expect u guys to give me all the goodies... even showing me all the
spawn areas helps... or who to look fer... fer quest n stuff like that....
anyway... im doing as much reading up on various sites b4 i start... so i
dont spend too much time trying to figure out what is what....
